description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 5 for East, 5 for South, and 8 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [63 Votes, Common]
